    report += "## Skills Used\n\n"
    for s in SKILLS_USED: report += f"### {s['name']}\n\n- **OS:** {s['os']}\n- **Layer:** {s['layer']}\n- **Purpose:** {s['purpose']}\n- **Input:** {s['input']}\n- **Output:** {s['output']}\n- **Verifier:** {s['verifier']}\n\n"
